WEBVTT

00:03:27.639 --> 00:03:30.150
Ba'zida unga "Pieta"ning
talabalari hamroh bo'lgan.

00:03:30.150 --> 00:03:34.680
Vivaldi ushbu Venetsiyadagi qizlar maktabi
musiqa ansambliga boshchilik qilgan.

00:03:34.680 --> 00:03:36.387
Ko'pchilik talabalar
yetim bo'lgan.

00:03:36.387 --> 00:03:40.677
Musiqiy ta'lim nafaqat yosh xonimlar uchun
mos ijtimoiy ko'nikma bo'lgan.

00:03:40.677 --> 00:03:42.658
Yaxshi oila qura olmagan qizlar uchun

00:03:42.658 --> 00:03:46.498
bu kelajakda mablag' manbai ham edi.

00:03:46.498 --> 00:03:48.459
Hatto bastakorning o'z davrida ham,

00:03:48.459 --> 00:03:50.919
Vivaldining musiqasi nafaqat zodagonlarni,

00:03:50.919 --> 00:03:53.708
balki hammani
kundalik tashvishlardan chalg'itgan.

00:03:53.708 --> 00:03:56.768
300 yil o'tsa ham hech narsa o'zgarmagan

00:03:56.768 --> 00:04:00.328
va hamon ham Vivaldining musiqasi 
yo'rtib yurayotgan otlardek yangraydi.